column2: "Challenge the new difficulty level. Though you might been used to it, things are different this time."
"The movements of the super hard hostiles will be different from those that you have experienced before."
"However, we cannot run just because we are afraid. Instead, we should clear and break through this challenge."
"I only need one thing from you. That is to clear this super hard Time Attack quest."
"You were requested because we think you can do it. I recommended you too. Now, good luck and do your best."
